messages.text:
Hey there! Thanks for getting my ABL file off reddit. If you’ve downloaded this, you’ve probably read the whole post, if not, this is a 10-team file with some fun modifications to play with. Everything was done within the file itself, so you can still get achievements! I hope you have fun with this, just don’t forget to pay close attention to finances, since you can get fired at any time. Have fun, see ya later!!

-ClevelandFan (/u/AmazingHenry)
